claim.claim-text:
A method for controlling movement of a vehicle (200), comprising:
identifying a current state (238) of the vehicle (200), wherein the current state (238) comprises a current location of the vehicle (200);
selecting, by a processor unit (1104), a next state (240) for the vehicle (200), wherein the next state (240) comprises a next location for the vehicle (200);
randomly selecting a value for an attribute of the next state (240) of the vehicle (200); and
controlling the movement of the vehicle (200) to move the vehicle (200) from the current state (238) to the next state (240).
